summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the Board of Public Works to purchase timber on Government lots 6, 7, and 8, on the Northeast quarter of the Northeast quarter of Section 18; the north half of Section 26; North half, Southwest quarter, north half, Southeast quarter of Section 28; east half, of the east half of Section 30, Township 22 North, Range 9 East, W.M., and providing the method of payment of paying the cost of acquiring the same.
